WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.491
Leading global enterprises introduces a unique challenge: the mechanics of

00:00:04.491 --> 00:00:08.983
trust and communication change drastically across borders. This brings up

00:00:08.983 --> 00:00:13.474
the critical competency of Cultural Intelligence, or CQ. CQ is

00:00:13.474 --> 00:00:17.966
a person's capability for successful adaptation to new cultural settings.

00:00:17.966 --> 00:00:22.457
While a Global Mindset allows for understanding the interdependence of

00:00:22.457 --> 00:00:26.949
the global economy, Cultural Intelligence focuses on the behavioral ability

00:00:26.949 --> 00:00:31.440
to interact interpersonally and bridge cultural differences.
